text: Aa en Hunze is a municipality of the province of Drenthe, the Netherlands. In 2016 about 25,000 people were living in this municipality. Aa en Hunze lies in the northeastern part of Drenthe. Aa en Hunze was established in 1998 by combining the municipalities of Anloo, Gasselte, Gieten, and Rolde. ==Other websites== * Aa en Hunze website Category:1990s establishments in the Netherlands Category:1998 establishments in Europe
